snippet.title: The Sims 3 Showtime -- Rise to Fame
snippet.description: Make your rise to fame in The Sims 3™ Showtime and live out the rags to riches story with your Sims as a singer, acrobat, magician... and moonlight as a DJ. Pre-order on Origin now: http://store.origin.com/store/ea/en_US/html/pbPage.sims3_showtime
